The Debian Package megacli-check-change
----------------------------

This package set cron job to check megacli RAID status and
 will send mail report on any changes.

"megacli" command is required.
It can be downloaded from official driver site or get packaged version
from http://hwraid.le-vert.net/ .

You need to install megacli command into /usr/sbin or /usr/local/sbin.

 -- Tatsuki Sugiura <sugi@nemui.org>  Thu, 11 Oct 2018 23:47:05 +0900
